== Kwakira ==
Ibirayi Potahto yakiriwe neza na rubanda, kubera intsinzi Shirley Frimpong-Manso yagezeho mbere. Filime yagaragaye 7.9 nabakoresha kuri Nollywood Reinvented.  Ibirayi Potahto yabonye imyiyerekano mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Durban ndetse n’Iserukiramuco rya Filimi [[Bwongereza|ry’Abongereza]]. Iyi filime kandi yagaragaye mu rwego rwo gutoranya iserukiramuco rya Filime [[Afurika]] kuva ku ya 27 Ukwakira kugeza 5 Ugushyingo. Ukuboza 2019, Potato Potahto yongewe kumugaragaro kurutonde rwa Netflix.
